  <description><![CDATA[<p>This great value, family-run hotel provides a convenient base for sampling the resort's restaurants, amenities and après ski. The Edelweiss offers comfortable accommodation in the homely, cosy atmosphere of the hotel with its attractive alpine decor in the bar and lounge. Expect a warm, genuine welcome from Bruno and his team. Small wonder that so many of our guests return here year after year! The fantastic central location means a walk of only 100m in the morning to join the ski lifts and ski school meeting point. At the end of the day, you can ski back to winthin 200m of hte hotel, via the lively après-ski area at the bottom of the piste. </p>]]></description>
